Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97744,99829}Meimi! Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:45.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100747,105001}The Tomb Stones are playing\Nat the Portside Concert Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105001,107754}– Really?\N– Tickets go on sale today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107754,108880}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108880,110798}You've never heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110798,113009}…of the Tomb Stones? They're hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:54.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113301,114510}Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116638,119015}You're so dense about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119015,121476}Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.44,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:125313,128441}{\an2\fad(1000,0)}All tickets sold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:11.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128566,131402}I see. Thank you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132654,134864}Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135448,138910}They sold out before noon.\NWe didn't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138910,140203}Oh, rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140203,143790}Hey, you girls!\NDid you come to buy tickets too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144082,145750}You guys too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145750,148503}Too bad. They're sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148836,150505}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152465,154258}She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154258,156969}We should have waited\Nin line last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:39.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156969,159013}It's a school day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159013,161974}{\an8}It's only one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159389,161974}What a bunch of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161974,163935}Rats! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:47.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164477,167397}They're making such a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:52.40,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:169232,172402}Danger, Do Not Touch!\NSuper Electric Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177156,178866}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179242,180535}Hi, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180535,183329}Hi, dear. Would you\Nlike some Russian tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183621,186040}No, maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187542,190002}What's wrong? Why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191003,192880}Don't worry. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:17.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193339,197719}You sure? All right.\NI'll show you a great trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:21.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197719,201514}It'll put a smile on any sad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201514,202890}That'd be terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211023,213526}You are now feeling happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213985,217989}That's right.\NSo happy you want to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:45.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219866,225204}Now you feel like laughing.\NYou're so happy, you want to burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:50.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225204,230960}You want to hug your dad\Nfor making you so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232086,235923}I think it's working.\NNow for the final touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235923,238926}– What?\N– Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:03.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239594,243389}Tickets to the Tomb Stones concert!\NHow did you get these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:10.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243848,250354}A client gave them to me, but I'm\Njust not into loud music like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250354,252440}I love you, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:17.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252440,257945}– They're not good seats, though.\N– That doesn't matter! Thanks, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257945,259822}She changes so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:26.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262825,266078}Two tickets. Who should I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:30.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266913,270750}Seira's not interested\Nin this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:37.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270750,277048}Kyoko and Ryoko would be thrilled,\Nbut they're bound to fight about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:42.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278966,282011}Sure, he would be happy to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282678,285223}But wouldn't it be\Nsort of like a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292438,294899}– Catch you later.\N– Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297693,300112}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302448,304992}– Good morning.\N– Too bad about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304992,307995}I was so upset, I couldn't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:11.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307995,311749}You liar, we're late because\Nyou overslept today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312542,314418}{\i1}I'm missing my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:18.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314418,318005}Hey, Emi!\NLet me see your homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318005,319799}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323594,325221}Oh, Haneoka, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328057,329684}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329684,331644}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331644,334438}If you have something to say, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334814,336899}– I have these tickets—\N– Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337400,339777}Asuka!\NYou're a Tomb Stones fan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339777,342238}Why do you wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:49.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345241,349579}– Tickets to the concert!\N– And front row seats too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:53.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349954,353165}– How did you get these?\N– From my uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353165,356544}– No way!\N– Hey, let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358004,360506}– How about it?\N– Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364385,366220}– Well?\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367096,368556}{\i1}What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368556,370641}{\i1}What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378274,380067}Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381611,383946}– What did you want?\N– Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383946,385531}Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386282,389869}– You started to say something.\N– Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389869,391329}Why the attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391329,395249}Rina will get mad if she\Ncatches you talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396667,398711}She's got nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399086,401464}Well, neither do l!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401756,403925}{\i1}What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404258,406302}{\i1}What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412475,414226}May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415269,417688}Forgive me for\Nentering unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418314,420691}That's quite all right.\NDo you have a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428574,430618}So you're a sculptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431786,435581}Yes, but I only make\Nmetal monuments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:20.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436207,440419}Aren't you Daisuke Noguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440419,443798}You were given many awards\Nat one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443798,445925}Yes, I had it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:30.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445925,450304}But I've been in a slump\Nfor some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:38.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452014,458145}I was recognized as a real sculptor\Nonly after I made the Steel Weathercock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:43.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458813,463275}Until then, I borrowed a space\Nin a workshop and did odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463275,466737}All I wanted was\Nto create a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:52.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469073,472785}But as soon as I unveiled\Nthe weathercock,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:57.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472785,477540}my life changed.\NAll my past hardships like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:05.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479291,485047}The Steel Weathercock\Nwas my lucky charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:10.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485047,490261}That's why I wouldn't sell it,\Nno matter how much anyone offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:14.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490261,494473}But it was stolen a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:20.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495683,500312}And I haven't been able\Nto finish a piece since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:24.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500312,504358}These past six months\Nhave been particularly bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:30.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504358,510906}Then recently I learned that my sculpture\Nis being displayed atop the Misato building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510906,513409}You must contact\Nthe building's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513659,516871}Of course I did that! But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523044,524754}Please give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525129,527506}The weathercock is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528049,531260}I believe you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:55.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531260,535222}I purchased that piece\Nfrom a legitimate art dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535514,537349}That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537349,538517}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:10.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545357,550112}That is the contract.\NWell? Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:14.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550780,554617}No, these documents aren't real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557453,560790}If you have complaints,\Ngo to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:24.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560790,564543}But I warn you, I do have the documents\Nto prove I bought the sculpture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:28.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564543,568547}There's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569381,572968}Unless, of course,\Nyou offer to buy it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:38.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572968,578516}However, I have promised to sell it to\Na businessman in Hong Kong next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578516,580142}So decide quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580768,583521}I beg you!\NI'm lost without my sculpture!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584021,586273}I must ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590319,593447}It's frustrating since\NI can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:57.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593447,597660}When will he sell it\Nto that businessman in Hong Kong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597660,602456}It will be removed three days\Nfrom now. I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603499,606418}And if he gets the sculpture back…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:10.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606877,610673}I'm sure he will be able\Nto create more pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610673,613634}But there's not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:18.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614677,618597}– Meimi? Meimi!\N– Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:23.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618597,623018}Are you okay? Since there's no time,\Nmaybe we should reconsider—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:28.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623018,628774}No! If we forsake a person in trouble,\Nwe'll damage St. Tail's reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628774,631068}I'll get it back for him at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:38.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633320,638075}The day after tomorrow.\NThe same night as the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:41.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638075,641745}Oh, well.\NIt won't be fun going alone anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:46.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643164,646083}I wonder what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646083,649712}Will he go to the concert, or…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651046,653674}I can't pull a job\Nwithout giving him a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659096,660014}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665728,668689}Asuka!\NWhat time should we meet today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:12.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669440,672318}– What are you talking about?\N– The concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672318,674403}Can't you go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:18.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674403,678866}I want you to come with me,\Nor give me back your ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679742,681410}Hey! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681410,683329}You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:28.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683954,688792}"I will steal the Steel Weathercock\Ntoday from the Misato building."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689168,690794}St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:36.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692129,696091}No, no, no! The concert's today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696091,698761}Forget about St. Tail!\NWe're going to the concert!
Comment: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:45.72,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:705726,705726}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:51.73,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:711732,711732}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:56.73,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:716737,716737}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717905,720741}St. Tail, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721367,723702}What a bothersome situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:07.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723702,727581}You must do your utmost\Nto capture her at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:10.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727581,730709}I'm completing the sale\Ntomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:14.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731210,734213}How did you come\Nto own that sculpture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734630,737675}I bought it, of course.\NFrom an art dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:21.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738008,741887}St. Tail never steals anything\Nfrom its rightful owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:25.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741887,745766}She's just a petty thief,\Nwith no reason for stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745766,748143}Or are you taking her side\Non this issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749520,752773}Listen, the mayor and I\Nare close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752773,755609}I can easily have you fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:41.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757236,761323}By the way, do you mind\Nletting me see that sculpture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:45.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761782,765035}By all means. I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:52.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766578,772668}This isn't good. If St. Tail is\Narrested, they'll know we stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:56.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772668,776005}Not if she can't talk\Nwhen she's captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783929,787766}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792813,793772}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796233,797443}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799445,801363}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817129,820716}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823218,824219}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:49.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824636,829183}For security, a high voltage current\Nruns through the sculpture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:51.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829475,831352}One touch and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832895,835147}Even St. Tail can't beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839651,842237}You're insane! She'll be—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842237,845657}All it means is a foolish\Nthief was electrocuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845657,847368}That's murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:10.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847368,850621}No matter. After all,\Nshe is just a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850621,852623}I won't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852623,855584}It's time for you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:19.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856001,859588}What are you doing? Let me go!\NHey, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859588,862049}You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867888,870057}What's wrong, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:33.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870057,873477}They said they don't\Nneed our protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875312,877940}But I'm not giving up that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:56.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892496,896792}Funny, no one's around. Maybe\Nhe went to the concert after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:03.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900712,903757}– Don't do anything, you got that?\N– Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917563,919106}Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929366,931452}It's wired with electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932327,934413}That fool! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:40.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936999,940294}So that's it! But for now…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940878,942045}Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:56.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949553,956560}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968739,970449}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970824,972951}You won't get away, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:15.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972951,975913}– Don't let her escape! After her!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980542,982085}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982628,983962}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988383,990511}She went into quadrant 24 C.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990511,992346}Shut her in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994681,997226}– Who's there?\N– Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:40.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997226,1000229}There was no one downstairs,\Nso I just came on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002022,1003732}You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:49.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006193,1009571}{\i1}Oh, no! I'll be locked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013825,1015911}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020999,1022543}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027047,1028173}I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032469,1034596}{\i1}Oh, no, I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037140,1039518}Where is St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040143,1042479}I'm sorry, but she escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042896,1045399}I believe my son came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:29.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045399,1049653}Yes, earlier, but he gave up and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:35.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051488,1055117}– Mr. President!\N– It's okay. He's about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058078,1059580}I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060831,1062207}Sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:47.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064876,1067212}We've trapped St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:51.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067212,1071091}Turn the cooler on.\NMake sure it's on full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071091,1073468}But Asuka Jr.'s in there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073468,1074261}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:04.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081727,1084187}It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086815,1089359}{\i1}I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:10.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089985,1090861}Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091945,1094698}This is for helping me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094698,1097826}{\i1}You helped me first, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098702,1100037}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:23.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100829,1103081}You've got a lot of guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103081,1104291}{\i1}So do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:29.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105626,1109838}There's this really headstrong girl\Nin my class too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:33.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109838,1113717}I don't know why,\Nbut we always end up fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:36.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113717,1116428}I don't mean to, it just happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116428,1118722}We had a fight today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118722,1121308}I don't know why, but she was mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121308,1122267}{\i1}You're so dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:46.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122893,1126229}But I could have been\Nto blame too. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:52.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128482,1132027}We've got to do something\Nor we'll freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132027,1134988}– Hey, son, you in there?\N– Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138033,1139201}{\i1}If I can break through that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:10.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147376,1150545}– Dad!\N– I knew you were up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150545,1152589}So where's St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157594,1158762}Rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159471,1162891}Stop! Come back here, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:26.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162891,1166937}I'm taking the sculpture!\NGive my best to your headstrong friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169231,1171608}Come back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:37.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173652,1177531}Things look bad.\NNow that Asuka Jr.'s out…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:41.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177531,1181118}If his father investigates,\Nwe're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181243,1184246}It seems the rumors were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184913,1187708}Your hobby is\Ncollecting stolen artwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187999,1189668}That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191086,1194381}You're not being cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196675,1198969}My God, look at all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198969,1201304}These are all listed as stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:05.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201304,1205517}You have quite a collection.\NMore than rumored!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205517,1206768}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219364,1220365}– Um…\N– Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:23.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220365,1223493}Hey, why are you two blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223493,1225370}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:29.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225370,1229916}Never mind that! Where were you\Nyesterday? I waited all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:33.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229916,1233670}Yesterday, St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237257,1239384}Were you two together last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239634,1242304}Don't be ridiculous!\NI wouldn't be caught dead—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:47.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244806,1247142}Hey, that hurts, Haneoka!
